    "summary": "<p>本期 Fork It 继续和大家探讨 Lightning Network。LN 在网络方面是怎么集大成的？它之前的诸多技术方案是什么？LN 因天时地利人和最终获得成功，这些因素又是什么呢？</p>\n\n<p>播客中还对 HTLC 和 Channel 构造等诸多技术进行了详细的分析，超 Hardcore，热爱技术的你一定不要错过～</p>\n\n<p>除了在泛用型播客客户端收听订阅《 Fork It 》，你还可以在<a href=\"https://www.ximalaya.com/keji/19792413/\" rel=\"nofollow\">喜马拉雅</a> 和<a href=\"https://music.163.com/#/djradio?id=792240368\" rel=\"nofollow\">网易云音乐</a>收听节目。</p>\n\n<p>What are you waiting for? Let’s Fork It!</p>\n\n<h3>ShowNotes</h3>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gavinandresen\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gavin Andresen</a> </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Craig_Steven_Wright\" rel=\"nofollow\">CSW </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://gavintech.blogspot.com/2012/07/off-chain-transactions.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gavin ' Blog  「Off-the-chain transactions」</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/MeniRosenfeld\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meni Rosenfeld</a> / <a href=\"https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=91732.0\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meni Rosenfeld's talk at Bitcointalk </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://bitcoin.org/en/glossary/signature-hash\" rel=\"nofollow\">SigHash</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cornwarecjp.github.io/amiko-pay/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Amiko Pay </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://bitpay.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bitpay</a> / <a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/bitpay-proposes-zero-confirmation-instant-payments-solution\" rel=\"nofollow\">Impulse </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.strawpay.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Strawpay</a> / <a href=\"https://www.strawpay.com/docs/stroem-factsheet.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stroem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.tik.ee.ethz.ch/file/716b955c130e6c703fac336ea17b1670/duplex-micropayment-channels.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Fast and Scalable Payment Network with Bitcoin Duplex Micropayment Channels</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_Wattenhofer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Roger Wattenhofer</a> / <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Snyke\" rel=\"nofollow\">Christian Decker</a> </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://lists.linuxfoundation.org/pipermail/bitcoin-dev/2015-December/011865.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gregory Maxwell 's Blog about Scale</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Timelock\" rel=\"nofollow\">Timelock</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Hash_Time_Locked_Contracts\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hash Time Locked Contract(HTLC)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zmnscpxj.github.io/offchain/generalized.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Funding Transactions</a> / <a href=\"https://bitcoin.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/ln-breach-remedy\" rel=\"nofollow\">Breach Remedy Transaction</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://webhdwallet.github.io/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HD Wallet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/lightningnetwork/lightning-rfc\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lightning RFC</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/lightningnetwork/lnd\" rel=\"nofollow\">LND</a> / <a href=\"https://github.com/mit-dci/lit\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lit</a> / <a href=\"https://github.com/ACINQ/eclair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eclair</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ElementsProject/lightning\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blockstream ElementsProject</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://monitor.firefox.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Firefox Monitor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://brave.com/kre925?gclid=CjwKCAjw_MnmBRAoEiwAPRRWW1mJ0n73Wtg7qfsJsoFR5kCSQN5l9ASv3VZcuL4yoEIi7euyDytWDRoCa54QAvD_BwE\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brave</a><br /></li>\n</ul>",
